{
  "stem": "1901.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't-- I still got marks on my legs, and I don't know what you got for sickness.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You die there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As long as you don't have typhus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Typhus was the one that died you, and-- and cholera and all those diseases.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Filth, it was all filth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, it was a few days later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He worked somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- yeah, we were together, in [? other ?] kommando, but he-- he-- he was quite capable.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he could play the piano, and he play the piano accordion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, after he came out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came out, in hospital I couldn't get near him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I saw him in hospital, I smuggled in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I start doing like a gardener, take a rake and start cleaning up and shouting everywhere.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I got him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was-- he survived, more or less there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, yeah, I was always nervous, of course, often.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nighttime.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, we came together-- Dutch by Dutch, Hungarians by Hungarians, and Greeks by Greeks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All had their own little groups.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very little [? and ?] work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very little [? and ?] work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was the other kommando.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] And I got later and better kommando, because-- when-- I talk about periods.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can tell from camp quite a few things that are from periods.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In-- in-- in Buna, Monowitz, then I could have an instrument.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't play in the marching out band, because they was full, but certainly we played amongst themselves.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to play for the SS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, oh, yes, they made evenings and we could play for them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Modern American music, they loved it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or German, you know, we'd play.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and they had-- in camp was in-- was in [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Puff. ?] You've heard about that too?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
